{"tid":193312,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［陰目偵信］召喚三哥","createTime":"2017-04-09T08:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T08:23:26.000Z","uid":48512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e55fb196348a31ca77936cf6f6fd39fddf8030","tid":193312,"uid":48512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"點解妖刀篇有變動？<br />\n1. 我記得起高登連載個陣，嚟搶刀郎個奸角座頭市，佢係學邪帝玩刀劍雙絕架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新書入面變左玩仗刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 我記得小太郎因爲有個和尚幫拖先打贏(呃走)座頭市，新書度又消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 小太郎借刀覆卓個把戚繼光苗刀，我記得之前有篇講陳近南寶劍故仔入面係個奸角陳十三用架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上幾點希望三哥上水指教下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/161452_c399cfc6e8f8b53fdf06f2fe1d6d104b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F161452_c399cfc6e8f8b53fdf06f2fe1d6d104b.jpg&h=0ea1086b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}